"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-football-olympiakos-vs-aston-villa-europa-conference-league-result-2024-b1156797.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Football  Aston Villa's European dream is over after losing toOlympiakosin the semi-final of theEuropa Conference League.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2180046079455e-27, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 259, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_European_Dream\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European dream\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_European_Dream\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_European_Dream\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa were eyeing a first European final since 1982 but, with the ancient Acropolis in the backdrop of the Stadio Georgios Karaiskakis, their hopes are now in ruins after a 6-2 aggregate defeat.\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 472, \"end\": 492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Karaiskakis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0750466980545674e-28, \"text\": \"Georgios Karaiskakis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Karaiskakis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Karaiskakis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They travelled to Athens needing a Herculean effort to overturn a 4-2 deficit from the first leg, but limped to a 2-0 defeat on the night, with last week's hat-trick hero Ayoub El Kaabi scoring the goals which sent the Greek side through to their first-ever European final.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 1.9852609388990105e-11, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}, {\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9944480849152052, \"rank\": 0.005552695410816245, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It concluded a miserable season on the continent for Premier League sides as there is no English representative in a final for the first time since 2019/20 and Unai Emery will see this as a huge missed opportunity to win a fifth European trophy in a tournament they were favourites for.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Unai Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will hope not be back in this third-tier competition any time soon as they can seal Champions League qualification at the weekend, which will cap an impressive season.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.359304622420888e-67, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Owner Evangelos Marinakis, who also owns Nottingham Forest, was seen celebrating his club reaching the final across the city at the home of deadly rivals AEK Athens in three weeks.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evangelos Marinakis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.286795009816967e-45, \"text\": \"Nottingham Forest\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.315456568082465e-21, \"text\": \"AEK\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 1.9852609388990105e-11, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa's hopes of a comeback were effectively ended after just 10 minutes as El Kaabi extended Olympiakos' lead to the sound of a near-defeaning noise.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1567, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.391356452501392e-28, \"text\": \"Olympiakos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Premier League side were sliced open by a long ball, former Wolves attacker Daniel Podence teed up Quini, whose cross was bundled home by El Kaabi.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.093621727876879e-33, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daniel Podence\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\"}, {\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Quini\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Resign today,' minister tells police chief in storm over Maccabi Tel Aviv fans ban  Spurs and Aston Villa slapped with misconduct charge after FA Cup brawl  Police chief admits misleading MPs in Maccabi Tel Aviv hearing after using AI tool  Little masterpieces: The ING Discerning Eye exhibition returns  Villa now had to find three goals just to send the tie to extra time and they had plenty of moments in the first half but were missing the quality when they needed it the most.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2180046079455e-27, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maccabi_Tel_Aviv_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.5154382216982303e-11, \"text\": \"Maccabi Tel Aviv\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maccabi_Tel_Aviv_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maccabi_Tel_Aviv_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9962432572019977, \"rank\": 0.0037709091329923396, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moussa Diaby broke through in the 30th minute after Leon Bailey had been fouled but home goalkeeper Kostas Tzolakis blocked his effort and then Douglas Luiz curled the free-kick over when play was brought back.\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moussa Diaby\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\"}, {\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leon Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Douglas Luiz\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tzolakis had to be at his best on the stroke of half-time to claw Bailey's deflected shot over as Villa pushed for one back before the break.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2540, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"score\": 0.9999550537778573, \"rank\": 4.494823499490648e-05, \"text\": \"Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They went for it in the second with Jhon Duran tamely shooting at Tzolakis and Ezri Konsa heading over from a corner.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2696, \"end\": 2706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ezri Konsa\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were becoming increasingly desperate, but still could not create any clear-cut chances and the hosts took advantage of big gaps at the back.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And El Kaabi's fifth goal of the tie in the 81st minute killed it as he raced clear and powered past Emiliano Martinez.\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2984, \"end\": 3001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Mart\\u00ednez\", \"score\": 0.9999999728756851, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emiliano Martinez\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Mart\\u00ednez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Mart\\u00ednez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was initially ruled out for offside but VAR overturned the decision.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3046, \"end\": 3049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.491197541485062e-49, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa had nowhere to go as they suffered a Greek tragedy, with their Europa Conference League campaign ending in a different part of Athens than they were wanting.\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3119, \"end\": 3132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_tragedy\", \"score\": 0.9904226125866759, \"rank\": 0.009591182131369815, \"text\": \"Greek tragedy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_tragedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_tragedy\"}, {\"begin\": 3152, \"end\": 3169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6829791643274487e-44, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}, {\"begin\": 3209, \"end\": 3215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 1.9852609388990105e-11, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 4119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3301, \"end\": 3310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9762331728611916, \"rank\": 0.02398308540208573, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://